{
  "stem": "4272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was like a-- a transit place, you know, that everybody was-- they rushed everybody down from that-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] there were broken legs and broken arms, and the German pushed them down and they couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then was a little opening, like a little door, and the SS men were standing on both sides in lines with canes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there wasn't a single-- we all had to go through that gate, the little gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there wasn't a single one that wasn't hit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of my girlfriends that-- she actually bore my same maiden-- same maiden name as I did, they hit us so hard in the back of the head that, in no time, she started vomiting and she died.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is while you were in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that transit camp, sort of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Transit camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father was hit, and I ran after him like helping him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the SS man ran after us, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father said, get away, get away, you'll get hit, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they kept us there about two-- two to three days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they put us on trains and took us south to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where I wound out in Bodzyntyn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's near Kielce.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could you spell that, please?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, Bodzyntyn?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "B-O-D-Z-Y-N-T-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what kind of a place was this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very small little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, more than a village, but a very small town with-- I-- I don't recall what the population of Jews was there, but we were-- they were already-- they were not in a ghetto yet, no.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh-uh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were put wherever with a family, wherever they could find a place for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- they separated families, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
